Installation:

  HTTP method
  git clone https://github.com/MTen/dotvim.git ~/.vim
  SSH method
  git clone git@github.com:MTen/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:
  ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Install pathogen.vim
  mkdir -p ~/.vim/autoload ~/.vim/bundle && \
  curl -LSso ~/.vim/autoload/pathogen.vim https://tpo.pe/pathogen.vim

Install git submodules
  git submodule init
  git submodule update


Adding new modules
cd .vim/bundle
git submodule add [github url] bundle/[submodule_dir]  #clones git repository to specified bundle directory
 
